\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93But an explosion this big should have sent things further. How faulty was that bomb?\u8221\'94}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (A flickering light catches my eye. There\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s a piece of shrapnel hugging the curb.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Hm. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s not the kind of shrapnel common to dirty bombs. Maybe HQ can tell me where it comes from.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Someone would have noticed a bomb under the car, unless it was planted just before the explosion. If that\u8217\'92s the case, it might be on camera footage. HQ would have that tape.\u8221\'94}
