\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Without the car in view, the city hall is eerily quaint. There\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s a camera above the astroturf, and an alley down the street.)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
